### Solve for $\maroonD{\ell}$



[[☃ image 1]]

$\begin{align}
\dfrac{\maroonD{\ell}}{\sqrt{145}} &= \dfrac{\blueE{0.8}}{\blueE{1}}
\\\\
\maroonD{\ell} &= 0.8 \cdot \sqrt{145}
\\\\
\maroonD{\ell} &\approx 9.63\,\text{m}
\end{align}$

(rounded to the nearest hundredth of a meter)

### Solve for $\ell$



